parameters: As expected of Captain-san! Incredibly strong!
That was a breeze, good work~

It must be nice to have it easy just watching from the
sidelines.
My job ends here. Now, strip the materials for the report.
That's a bit cold, isn't it? We hunted so well together.
True, I was just watching from behind.
I thought Captain-san looked so cool fighting.
Is that so? I don't mind being praised.

Well, of course. There's a certain way a swordsman should
carry themselves.
It seems some of it has rubbed off on you just by watching.

I mean, you looked cool and all, but I couldn't help
noticing your butt...\I[12]

I've been thinking for a while now, but Captain-san, you've
got a nice ass, you know?\I[12]

To be honest, I got excited, so could you help me out with a
quick one here?\I[12]
Are you an idiot!? How did it come to this kind of talk!?
But, you know, when it's hard, can't help it, right?\I[12]

So I've decided to take care of today's dick business right
here, okay?\I[12]
You... deciding things on your own...

If you say do it, I can't refuse... but whatever happens, I
don't want to know...
